 class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>module</h3>\n<p>적용할 모듈을 명시</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>test: /\\.jsx?/</code> - js와 jsx에 적용한다</li>\n<li>loader - 적용할 rule</li>\n<li>\n<p>options - rule의 옵션</p>\n<ul>\n<li>presets와 plugins는 아래 예시처럼 나눠서 작성</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"json\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">module: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">rules</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">: [{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">test</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">/\\.jsx?$/</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">loader</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">&#39;babel-loader&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-4 grvsc-tiszgT-i grvsc-tiszgT-u grvsc-t4tStz-7\">options</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><sp